===Etymology===
{{Han etyl}}
{{liushu|p}}, originally a stylized picture of clouds. The character was subsequently borrowed for a [[homophone]] meaning "say" and the original meaning came to be represented by [[雲]] through the addition of a [[semantic]] [[雨]] ("[[rain]]") component.

The simplified form adopted by the [[People's Republic of China]] in the 1950s eliminates this later addition and uses 云 for both "say" and "cloud".

